.starfield_update
    SEC
    LDY #&00
    LDX #&00
    LDA data_1307
    EOR #&50
    STA data_1307
    ASL data_1308
.L1319
    LDA starfield_type,X
    CMP #&02
    BNE L136C
    LDA starfield_pos_lo,X
