.enemy_bullet_collide_player
    LDA enemy_bullet_x,X  \ Box-collision test for one enemy_bullet against the player. Hit window: player_x in [bullet_x, bullet_x+5] AND player_y in [bullet_y, bullet_y+&10]. On hit: erase the 2×2 bullet trail with lev_erase_brush+&102, mark the slot inactive (&FF), and fall through into lose_a_life.
    STA zp_test_x
    LDA enemy_bullet_y,X
    STA zp_test_y
    LDA zp_player_x
    CMP zp_test_x
    BCC L1DB2
    RTS
.L1DB2
    LDA zp_player_x
    ADC #&05
    CMP zp_test_x
    BCC L1DBD
    JMP L1DBE
.L1DBD
    RTS
.L1DBE
    LDA zp_player_y
    CMP zp_test_y
    BCC L1DBD
    SBC #&10
    CMP zp_test_y
    BCC L1DCB
    RTS
.L1DCB
    LDY enemy_bullet_y,X
    LDA enemy_bullet_x,X
    TAX
    JSR calc_screen_addr
    LDX #&02
    LDY #&02
    LDA #LO(lev_erase_brush + &102)
    STA sprite_src_lo
    LDA #HI(lev_erase_brush + &102)
    STA sprite_src_hi
    JSR sprite_plot_xy
    LDX data_16F5
    LDA #&FF
    STA enemy_bullet_x,X

.lose_a_life
    STX data_16F5  \ Per-hit handler — runs once each time the player ship is touched by a hazard / enemy / bullet (see check_player_collisions). Plays OSWRCH 7 (the redefined BBC bell). Toggles lives_blink_state (0↔1) and DECs player_hp on every other call — so player_hp drops by 1 per actual death, with the blink toggle in between giving a two-frame red/yellow flash on the ship icon at the bottom of the screen. The icon is redrawn at column (player_hp + &1F), row &5F, using gfx_icon_03 (state 0) or the alternate icon at &48B8 (state 1). When player_hp hits 0 AND the blink-toggle says state 1, JMP death_anim (= explosion + DEC lives_left + init).
    LDA #&07
    JSR OSWRCH
    LDA lives_blink_state
    EOR #&01
    STA lives_blink_state
    CMP #&00
    BNE L1E05
    DEC player_hp
.L1E05
    LDA player_hp
    ADC #&1F
    LDY #&5F
    TAX
    JSR calc_screen_addr
    LDA #&48
    STA sprite_src_hi
    LDA #LO(gfx_icon_03)
    STA sprite_src_lo
    LDY lives_blink_state
    CPY #&00
    BNE L1E2B
    LDA #HI(gfx_icon_03)
    STA sprite_src_hi
    LDA #&B8
    STA sprite_src_lo
.L1E2B
    LDX #&01
    LDY #&08
    JSR sprite_plot_xy
    LDA player_hp
    BEQ L1E3B
    LDX data_16F5
    RTS
.L1E3B
    LDA lives_blink_state
    CMP #&01
    BEQ death_anim
    LDX data_16F5
    RTS

